you can pass `this` into new Worker() and make it a private property of worker. So: `public MainWindow()
    {
        InitializeComponent();
        Worker worker = new Worker(this);
        worker.run_Worker();
    }`

`class Worker{
private MainWindow lthis{get;set;} 
 public Worker(MainWindow lthis){
   this.lthis = lthis;
}

}`

